"{\"uid\": \"tribune.com.pk-story-2488203-governor-sindh-honours-olympic-gold-medallist-arshad-nadeem-with-rs20m-reward\", \"text\": \"EC  Kamran Tessori praised Arshad Nadeem's dedication and a grand reception was hosted for him at Governor House  Olympic gold medallist Arshad Nadeem was warmly welcomed by Governor Sindh Kamran Khan Tessori at the Governor House on Wednesday.  The reception was held in honour of Arshad's historic achievement, with the Governor announcing a cash reward of Rs2\\u00a0million for the national hero.  During the event, Governor Tessori praised Arshad's dedication, stating that the entire nation stands behind him.  He credited Arshad's success to the prayers of his parents and highlighted the significance of his victory for Pakistan.  \\\"Arshad Nadeem has brought great joy to the nation after a long time,\\\" the Governor remarked.  The event saw a large gathering of people from across Sindh, including businessmen who announced additional rewards and incentives for Nadeem.  Governor Kamran also shared that the Sindh government would contribute Rs50 million, with a total of Rs100 million being collected from the Governor House.  Arshad, expressing his gratitude, thanked the people of Karachi for their overwhelming support and the.  He also expressed appreciation for the live coverage by the media, which allowed the entire nation to share in the celebrations.  COMMENTS  Comments are moderated and generally will be posted if they are on-topic and not abusive.  For more information, please see ourComments FAQ  This material may not be published, broadcast, rewritten,                     redistributed or derived from. Unless otherwise stated, all content is                     copyrighted \\u00a9 2025 The Express Tribune.\"}"